"                      ╭ keys ──────────────────────────────────────╮   guide              "
"  PIPELINE ───────────│                                            │──────────────────────"
"  ○ spec              │ navigate                                   │                      "
"  ○ plan              │   j/k  move                                │                      "
"  ○ plan-review       │   [ ]  cycle features                      │▄▄                    "
"  ○ tests-red         │   tab 1-5  panes                           │  v e r i f y         "
"  ○ implement         │   g/G  top / follow                        │                      "
"  ○ dual-review       │                                            │ts → impl → dual      "
"                      │ run                                        │ spec or plan live    "
" 󰚩 AGENTS ────────────│   enter  run stage / open                  │tach · a takeover     "
"  󰚩 claude …          │   s  chat: edit spec/plan                  │kfix · o nvim         "
"  󰚩 codex …           │   a  take over session                     │s · --force           "
"  󱘖 bridge …          │   x  cancel run                            │in · repro            "
"   nvim —             │   c/C  check fast / full                   │it codes              "
"   check ?            │                                            │h features            "
"                      │ findings                                   │an · pr-comment       "
"   detached           │   f  mark fixed (toggle)                   │ips, in-app           "
"                      │   d  dismiss (toggle)                      │                      "
"                      │   v  show/hide resolved                    │?  keys    q  quit    "
"                      │                                            │                      "
"                      │ tools                                      │                      "
